**Title:** COM - BadgeLife Community - SAINTCON

**URL:** [https://saintcon.org/com-badgelife-community/](https://saintcon.org/com-badgelife-community/)

**Description:** 
The BadgeLife Community is associated with SAINTCON and emphasizes a collaborative approach. The information is provided by various contributors including Compukidmike, Redactd, Klipper, V0rtex, Mike's Wife, and BP. It emphasizes the excitement surrounding badges and the active participation of the community.

**Main Features:**
- **Event Information:**
  - It highlights that the community will be unveiling something new and exciting this year.

- **MiniBadge Details:**
  - A MiniBadge will be available to visitors at the community booth.

- **Desktop Wallpaper:**
  - The community offers downloadable desktop wallpapers.

**Hours of Operation:**
- **Expo Closed:** Monday
- **Tuesday to Wednesday:** 10:30 AM - 5:00 PM
- **Thursday to Friday:** 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM (Friday 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM)

**Additional Community Links:**
- Communities include AI, AppSec, Blueteam, Hardware Hacking, Health Care Hacking, ID-IOT, LockPick, RFID/NFC, Space, Tamper Evident, The Keep, V.E.N.D, WiC Advocates, Briefs, Education Security, Ham Radio, and HomeLabs.
  
- Upcoming events include Application Security Jeopardy, Job Fair, and Hack In The Box.

**Visuals:**
- Logos and promotional images related to Badgelife are included, emphasizing branding.

**Social Engagement:**
- The community encourages joining on Discord and offers educational content regarding MiniBadges.

**Footer Information:**
- Includes links for Code of Conduct, FAQs, Registration Terms, Support, Resources, and previous events listings.

